high_descs: Turn left to go to the counter on the right of the stove.
Pick up the potato in the corner of the counter.
Turn around to go to the left side of the white table.
Place the potato on the table.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Slice the potato on the table.
Place the knife on the right of the potato.
Take one slice of potato.
Turn to go to the microwave above the stove.
Microwave the potato slice and take it out.
Turn around and go to the trash can between the sink and the refrigerator.
Place the potato inside the trash can.

high_descs: Walk forward, turn left and walk to the counter, turn right.
Pick up potato on left side of counter.
Turn right, walk to the end, turn right and walk to the kitchen table.
Place potato on top of horizontal knife blade.
Pick up knife from underneath potato.
Cut the potato on the table into slices.
Place the knife on table to the right of the potato.
Take the first slice of potato closest to the table edge.
Turn right to walk out of the corner and head to the kitchen stove.
Open the microwave above the stove and place the potato slice inside. Close the door and heat up the potato, then remove the potato.
Turn around and head to the trash can between the fridge and counter.
Place the potato slice into the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Heat up a sliced potato and place into the trash can.
